OL,3,CCustomers to get compensation after
OL,4,Cdays of disruption to water supply
OL,6,FHouseholds in Rhondda Cynon Taf
OL,7,Faffected by the 'boil water' warning
OL,8,Fwill be offered financial compensation
OL,9,Fby Dwr Cymru Welsh Water.
OL,11,FIt comes after a burst pipe at Maerdy
OL,12,FWater Treatment Works on Thursday (21
OL,13,FMay) caused a safety risk with the
OL,14,Fwater quality, meaning nearby
OL,15,Fcustomers have been told to boil tap
OL,16,Fwater before drinking and cooking.
OL,18,FThe issue has since been repaired, but
OL,19,Fthe firm have placed Rhondda customers
OL,20,Funder 3 different zones to show when
OL,21,Fthe notice can be lifted:
OL,26,@qD@Es{
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
