PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779981070
OL,3,CCustomers to get compensation after
OL,4,Cdays of disruption to water supply
OL,6,FCustomers affected will now receive
OL,7,Fcompensation.
OL,9,FIn an update on their website, Dwr
OL,10,FCymru Welsh Water explained that
OL,11,Fhousehold customers will receive #40
OL,12,Fonce the notice has been in place for
OL,13,F48 hours, with a further #20 for every
OL,14,Fadditional 24 hours after that.
OL,16,FNon-household customers will receive
OL,17,F#60 once the notice has been in place
OL,18,Ffor 48 hours, with a further #40 for
OL,19,Fevery additional 24 hours after that.
