OL,3,CCustomers to get compensation after
OL,4,Cdays of disruption to water supply
OL,6,FThe firm also added that they aim to
OL,7,Fmake payments within 10 working days.
OL,9,FIn a letter, Steve Wilson, Chief
OL,10,FOperations Officer for Welsh Water,
OL,11,Fapologised for the issue caused:
OL,13,F"We are very sorry for the worry and
OL,14,Fdisruption caused by the precautionary
OL,15,Fboil water notice affecting customers
OL,16,Fsupplied by Maerdy Water Treatment
OL,17,FWorks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
