PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779981070
OL,3,CCustomers to get compensation after
OL,4,Cdays of disruption to water supply
OL,6,F"This phased approach reflects the
OL,7,Ftime it takes for fully treated water
OL,8,Fto move through each part of the
OL,9,Fsystem and for test results to confirm
OL,10,Fit is safe to lift the notice.
OL,12,F"We will send messages to customers'
OL,13,Fphones (where they've registered their
OL,14,Fdetails with us) to confirm the end of
OL,15,Fthe boil notice in their area."
OL,17,FWelsh Water says more information is
OL,18,Favailable at dwrcymru.com.
